Paternal great-grandfather had colorectal cancer in his 80s.  Paternal great-grandmother had astrocytoma in her 70s, and a paternal great-aunt had astrocytoma at age 54.  Paternal great-uncle had lung cancer.  Another paternal great-uncle had colon cancer at age 70.

